Package: withmargins
Title: Summarize and Expand Data with Margins
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Yusuke", "Sasaki", , "sayuks.dev@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Summarize data with margins (totals) and expand data by treating margins as category levels. Supports 'tidyverse' workflows for analysis.
